</script><p>Yet through it all, Bruno carried with him his determination and will to triumph over the odds. Here is the story of his remarkable life.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Escaping death</strong></p><div id="native_top" data-ad="native_top" class="native_top gpt_ads"></div><script>
BidBarrel.setSizeMappings("native_top",
[
{
viewport: [0, 0],
sizes: [[11, 11], "fluid"]
},
{
viewport: [300, 0],
sizes: [[11, 11], "fluid"]
},
{
